Title: Object: The Flight into Egypt
Description: Joseph leads the Virgin on a donkey towards the left. A thunderstorm overhead. Fourth state. 1891 Etching
Bibliographic references: Strang 1962 / William Strang, catalogue of his etchings and engravings (207)
Strang 1906-23 / William Strang, catalogue of his etched work (170)
Acquisition notes: Bought by Dodgson himself for the BM. He reported that the lot of 32 prints was cheap and 'included a number of rare states and one etching wholly unknown and unique, in addition to several which are common but not yet represented in the BM.'
